1
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:26,260
You piece of trash!

2
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:28,260
You can't even catch a street rat.

3
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:29,720
You're utterly incompetent!

4
00:01:29,720 --> 00:01:30,980
Utterly incompetent!

5
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:32,000
I, Hu Wenyi,

6
00:01:32,320 --> 00:01:33,979
do not have such a useless son!

7
00:01:34,720 --> 00:01:35,280
Dad.

8
00:01:35,320 --> 00:01:36,320
That slum,

9
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:38,960
it's crowded and has complicated paths.

10
00:01:38,960 --> 00:01:40,759
It's already hard to search and arrest someone there.

11
00:01:40,759 --> 00:01:41,960
Plus, that Wang Song

12
00:01:41,960 --> 00:01:43,479
is like a sneaky monkey.

13
00:01:43,479 --> 00:01:45,280
It's too difficult to catch him.

14
00:01:45,520 --> 00:01:46,240
Shut up!

15
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:50,880
Mr. Yamamoto.

16
00:01:51,600 --> 00:01:53,600
We still haven't caught the arsonist.

17
00:01:53,600 --> 00:01:54,479
What do you think

18
00:01:54,479 --> 00:01:56,479
we should do next?

19
00:01:57,759 --> 00:01:59,880
He was lucky to escape this time,

20
00:02:00,240 --> 00:02:02,080
so he'll probably lay low for a while

21
00:02:02,080 --> 00:02:03,720
and won't cause any more trouble.

22
00:02:03,720 --> 00:02:04,800
No need to rush.

23
00:02:14,480 --> 00:02:16,010
Miss Hu, please take a look.

24
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:18,720
This is...

25
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:22,440
The mastermind behind your attempted kidnapping at the teahouse that day,

26
00:02:22,440 --> 00:02:23,560
I have already caught him.

27
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:24,880
According to his confession,

28
00:02:24,880 --> 00:02:25,960
your father's death

29
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:26,960
has another hidden truth.

30
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:28,000
Before Zhinian left,

31
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:29,960
he went to Xiuning and collected some evidence,

32
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,520
and he asked me to hand it to you personally.

33
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:32,640
The evidence in this wooden box

34
00:02:32,640 --> 00:02:34,160
is related to Hu Wenyi.

35
00:02:34,440 --> 00:02:35,320
Hu Wenyi.

36
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:08,060
Don't move.

37
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:10,240
I have questions for you.

38
00:03:10,720 --> 00:03:11,480
Spare my life.

39
00:03:11,480 --> 00:03:12,280
Don't kill me!

40
00:03:12,760 --> 00:03:13,520
Ask away.

41
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,920
Where is the Hu family's black tea recipe?

42
00:03:15,920 --> 00:03:16,440
Speak!

43
00:03:17,440 --> 00:03:18,240
I'll tell you!

44
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,440
Don't kill me!

45
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:34,800
Mr. Hu,

46
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:36,840
I mentioned to you before

47
00:03:37,079 --> 00:03:38,280
about the recipe.

48
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:39,760
When will it be ready?

49
00:03:39,920 --> 00:03:40,560
Oh,

50
00:03:43,040 --> 00:03:44,160
about that.

51
00:03:44,480 --> 00:03:46,680
I've already sent someone to handle it.

52
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:47,640
You just need to

53
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:48,770
wait a few more days.

54
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:51,160
Mr. Hu,

55
00:03:51,720 --> 00:03:54,579
do you not want to cooperate with me, Toru Yamamoto?

56
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:56,840
No.

57
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:57,920
Mr. Yamamoto,

58
00:03:58,079 --> 00:03:59,360
you misunderstood.

59
00:03:59,720 --> 00:04:00,380
Even though

60
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:01,960
I am the head of the family,

61
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:04,120
I still need to pull some strings.

62
00:04:04,920 --> 00:04:06,200
I beg you, Mr. Yamamoto,

63
00:04:06,200 --> 00:04:07,720
give me a few more days.

64
00:04:12,880 --> 00:04:14,960
Since you said so, Mr. Hu,

65
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,920
then we will

66
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:18,640
wait a few more days.

67
00:04:18,640 --> 00:04:19,640
Thank you, Mr. Yamamoto.

68
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:22,440
I will definitely give you a satisfactory answer.

69
00:04:25,080 --> 00:04:27,480
I still have business matters to deal with,

70
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:29,320
so I won't bother you anymore today.

71
00:04:29,320 --> 00:04:29,850
Alright.

72
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:31,400
Mr. Yamamoto,

73
00:04:31,400 --> 00:04:32,000
take care.

74
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:33,200
I won't see you out.

75
00:04:33,200 --> 00:04:34,000
Mr. Yamamoto.

76
00:04:37,960 --> 00:04:39,440
Giving you the secret recipe

77
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:41,700
would be cutting off my source of wealth.

78
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:42,560
Hmph.

79
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:53,409
Clan elders.

80
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:07,560
Master.

81
00:05:08,400 --> 00:05:09,000
Come here.

82
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:11,600
I've searched everywhere,

83
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:13,600
but couldn't find the young master.

84
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,480
That useless son,

85
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:18,840
where did he go?

86
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:22,520
Let's go.

87
00:05:24,880 --> 00:05:25,800
Miss,

88
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:27,160
it's getting late.

89
00:05:27,280 --> 00:05:29,340
We should head to the ancestral hall.

90
00:05:29,440 --> 00:05:31,040
Today we must win

91
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:32,480
the clan elders' support.

92
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:34,600
Don't act on impulse.

93
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,120
Hu Wenyi,

94
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:38,400
for the pain

95
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:40,290
and humiliation you caused me,

96
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:41,640
today

97
00:05:41,880 --> 00:05:43,320
I will make you

98
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:45,040
pay for it all.

99
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,040
Mr. Yamamoto.

100
00:06:11,760 --> 00:06:12,560
Found it.

101
00:06:42,520 --> 00:06:44,159
Well done.

102
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:47,100
You flatter me, Mr. Yamamoto.

103
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:49,960
Let's go.

104
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:13,400
Oh no.

105
00:07:26,640 --> 00:07:27,360
Elders.

106
00:07:29,320 --> 00:07:30,080
Everyone.

107
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:34,760
Elders.

108
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:36,120
Please.

109
00:07:44,080 --> 00:07:45,000
Today,

110
00:07:45,280 --> 00:07:47,880
I invited you all to the ancestral hall

111
00:07:48,080 --> 00:07:49,040
mainly to

112
00:07:49,159 --> 00:07:51,280
witness

113
00:07:51,960 --> 00:07:54,690
Hu Wenyi taking over as the new head of the family.

114
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:55,880
I hope

115
00:07:56,159 --> 00:07:57,040
Wenyi,

116
00:07:57,400 --> 00:07:59,060
after taking over as the head,

117
00:07:59,280 --> 00:08:02,240
can lead the Hu clan

118
00:08:02,520 --> 00:08:04,520
to abide by the ancestral teachings

119
00:08:04,840 --> 00:08:06,560
and revitalize the family business.

120
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:07,320
Hereby,

121
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:09,320
I announce

122
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:11,800
that starting today,

123
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:13,560
Hu Wenyi

124
00:08:14,400 --> 00:08:15,440
will succeed.

125
00:08:15,440 --> 00:08:15,920
Wait.

126
00:08:17,880 --> 00:08:18,720
Hu Linglong.

127
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:24,320
I, Hu Linglong,

128
00:08:24,320 --> 00:08:25,080
do not agree.

129
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:29,440
Elders.

130
00:08:29,440 --> 00:08:30,000
Yeah.

131
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:35,240
Hu Wenyi

132
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:36,280
is full of evil

133
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:37,440
and deeply sinful.

134
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:39,799
How can a treacherous person like him

135
00:08:39,799 --> 00:08:42,530
be worthy of taking over the ancestral heritage?

136
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:44,540
The way of heaven is clear.

137
00:08:46,280 --> 00:08:49,080
How can he tarnish the position of the family head?

138
00:08:49,280 --> 00:08:50,240
Hu Linglong,

139
00:08:51,280 --> 00:08:52,960
your mother just died for you,

140
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:55,650
and you are causing trouble again.

141
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:57,960
In front of the ancestors,

142
00:08:58,320 --> 00:08:59,380
you speak nonsense

143
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:00,960
and refuse to change.

144
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:02,200
Today,

145
00:09:02,640 --> 00:09:04,560
let's see who can take your place.

146
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:06,200
Guards.

147
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:06,720
Here.

148
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:08,120
Beat them

149
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:09,160
with sticks

150
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:11,080
and throw them out of the ancestral hall.

151
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:12,210
After the ceremony,

152
00:09:12,800 --> 00:09:14,330
I, as the head of the family,

153
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:15,640
will deal with them myself.

154
00:09:15,640 --> 00:09:16,280
Wait.

155
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:22,920
Hu Wenyi.

156
00:09:24,280 --> 00:09:26,540
When I took over as the head of the family,

157
00:09:26,920 --> 00:09:28,280
you interfered and obstructed

158
00:09:28,280 --> 00:09:30,240
on the grounds that I disguised as a man

159
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:32,160
to deceive the clan.

160
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:34,960
I would like to ask everyone here,

161
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:37,080
if someone like me cannot inherit the position of family head,

162
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:37,680
how can he,

163
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:39,000
Hu Wenyi?

164
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:40,480
He burned down the tea house,

165
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:42,080
colluded with Japanese pirates,

166
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:42,920
poisoned his own brother,

167
00:09:42,920 --> 00:09:43,760
murdered for power,

168
00:09:43,760 --> 00:09:44,960
and betrayed the family.

169
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,560
Such a purely evil and wicked person,

170
00:09:46,560 --> 00:09:47,160
can he?

171
00:09:47,560 --> 00:09:48,820
This is pure nonsense!

172
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:50,440
Nonsense?

173
00:09:51,120 --> 00:09:51,840
Hu Wenyi,

174
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:53,680
how can you be so sure

175
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:56,480
that I don't have evidence in my hands?

176
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:58,360
Stop bluffing here.

177
00:10:00,040 --> 00:10:01,200
What are you waiting for?

178
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:02,120
Do it now!

179
00:10:02,520 --> 00:10:03,160
Wait!

180
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:04,920
Half a month ago, I was indeed at the tea plantation,

181
00:10:04,920 --> 00:10:06,480
and had a dispute with the British merchants.

182
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:07,360
But there was a reason.

183
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:08,440
They caused trouble and hit people.

184
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:10,760
You Japanese do evil things on Chinese soil.

185
00:10:10,760 --> 00:10:12,520
We will never cooperate with you.

186
00:10:12,520 --> 00:10:13,320
Please leave.

187
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:17,240
Elders...

188
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,480
If

189
00:10:21,880 --> 00:10:23,240
we let a villain usurp the position

190
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:24,480
and wicked people take charge,

191
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:25,680
then our Hu family

192
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:28,040
will bring about its own destruction.

193
00:10:28,040 --> 00:10:28,680
Wenyi.

194
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:29,760
Let me ask you.

195
00:10:30,160 --> 00:10:31,960
Is what Hu Linglong just said

196
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:32,840
true

197
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:33,920
or false?

198
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,080
That Hu Linglong

199
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:37,490
dares to lie in front of our ancestors!

200
00:10:37,520 --> 00:10:38,800
Whatever she says,

201
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:41,760
you absolutely must not believe!

202
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:44,130
Since you have a clear conscience,

203
00:10:44,520 --> 00:10:47,050
then the evidence Hu Linglong just mentioned

204
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:48,360
is all fabricated.

205
00:10:48,680 --> 00:10:49,280
Yes.

206
00:10:50,920 --> 00:10:51,880
Hu Linglong.

207
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:54,200
Regarding Wenyi's many crimes,

208
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:55,160
do you have

209
00:10:55,240 --> 00:10:57,300
any witnesses or physical evidence?

210
00:10:59,760 --> 00:11:00,440
Elder.

211
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:02,560
Here is the physical evidence.

212
00:11:02,560 --> 00:11:03,600
As for the witness,

213
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:04,800
the witness is here.
